f:\mathbb{R}P^k\to\mathbb{R}P^\infty
\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z}
\tilde{f}:S^k\to S^\infty
k\geq 2
f_\#
 (1)\;f\text{ lifts to a }\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z}\text{- equivariant map} \iff f_\#:\pi_1(\mathbb{R}P^k)\to \pi_1(\mathbb{R}P^\infty) \text{ is an isomorphism} \; (2) 
\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z}
(1)\iff f_*:H_k(\mathbb{R}P^k;\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z})\to H_k(\mathbb{R}P^\infty;\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z})\text{ is an isomorphism}\quad (3)
(1)\iff f_*:H_i(\mathbb{R}P^k;\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z})\to H_i(\mathbb{R}P^\infty;\mathbb{Z}/2\mathbb{Z})\text{ is an isomorphism for }i\leq k \quad (4)
